.TH EMOJIS "1" "December 2025" "emojis 202208062250-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
emojis \- Interactive emoji picker and clipboard integration tool with dmenu/rofi support
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B emojis
[\fI\,COMMAND\/\fR] [\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B emojis
is an interactive emoji picker that displays and copies emojis to the clipboard. It integrates with dmenu/rofi for graphical emoji selection, supports piping and direct text emoji conversion, and uses the emojify utility for emoji substitution.
.PP
The script automatically downloads and manages the emojify binary, maintains a local emoji list, and provides multiple selection interfaces including graphical menus (dmenu/rofi), search functionality, and stdin pipe support.
.PP
emojis simplifies emoji usage by providing quick access to thousands of emojis with clipboard integration, eliminating the need to manually search for or remember emoji codes.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B emojis
Display dmenu/rofi picker to select and copy emoji to clipboard (default)
.TP
.B emojis dmenu
Explicitly open dmenu/rofi emoji picker interface
.TP
.B emojis search TERM [TERM...]
Search for emojis matching search terms
.TP
