Convert emoji codes in text (e.g., :heart:) to emojis and copy to clipboard
.TP
.B emojis list
Display complete list of all available emojis
.TP
.B emojis update
Update the emojify binary and regenerate emoji list
.TP
.B echo 'I :heart: you' | emojis
Pipe text with emoji codes for conversion to actual emojis
